      <h3>About Me</h3>
      <p>I'm Basti and I'm addicted. Addicted to traveling.
          I want to see the world while I'm still young, healthy and independent.
          Well, the "young" part might be debatable - I was born in 1982 after all.
          I originally come from northern Germany,
          but currently live and work in Ireland.
          I work in IT.
          So I'm a proper office worker, but not a nerd.
          Whether you believe it or not, I love my job almost as much as traveling.
          After all, it finances everything.
          I've already traveled to quite a few countries and seen quite a lot.</p>

      <h4>Countries I've Visited</h4>
      <p>Germany, Netherlands, Belgium, France, Spain, Portugal, Italy, Switzerland, Austria, Hungary,
          Czechoslovakia, Romania, Poland, Denmark, Ireland (ROI) &amp; Northern Ireland (NI), Scotland,
          England &amp; USA.</p>

